<body>

    <div class="bg-light">
        <div class="container py-5">
            <div class="row h-100 align-items-center py-5">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h1 class="display-4">Find Out About Us!</h1>
                    <p class="lead text-muted mb-0">
                        JDE Traders sell many different types of vehicles, which are dependent on
                        the level of client and their specific requirement.
                    </p>
                    <p class="lead text-muted mb-0">
                        They do howeverin hatchbacks and bakkies and also focus on low budget vehicles for the
                        average South African.
                    </p>
                    <p class="lead text-muted mb-0">
                        They sell categories of vehicles that include brand
                        new, pre-owned and non-running vehicles.
                    </p>

                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-6 d-none d-lg-block"><img src="~/Images/ford-mustang-boss-429-1970-by-simon-clay-news-photo-1598884238.jpg" style="width:100%"/></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white py-5">
        <div class="container py-5">
            <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-lg-6 order-2 order-lg-1">
                    <i class="fa fa-bar-chart fa-2x mb-3 text-primary"></i>
                    <h2 class="font-weight-light">
                        Shiela and her team focus mainly on obtaining the vehicles at cheap
                        purchase prices in order to sell them for an appealing price to the public.
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-italic text-muted mb-4">
                        They also allow potential customers to request a specific type of vehicle, and
                        will use this to track the vehicle down.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5 px-5 mx-auto order-1 order-lg-2" >
                    <img src="~/Images/dims.jpg" style="width:100%" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-5 px-5 mx-auto">
                    <img src="~/Images/appr_banner.jpg" style="width:100%"/>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    
                    <h2 class="font-weight-light">
                        They constantly monitor vehicles put up
                        for sale online and travel around Gauteng in order to complete purchase
                        transactions by fetching the vehicles from sellers.
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-italic text-muted mb-4">
                        They take an online
                        approach to their marketing strategy, which allows them to target specific
                        areas and specific customer types depending on the vehicle.
                    </p>
                        <p class="font-italic text-muted mb-4">
                            When vehicles
                            are sold, customers have to pick it up from JDE Traders, as they do not offer
                            deliveries.
                        </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
